data.name: Create Delivery
data.description: There are three required parameters. First one is recipient  phone number and the second one is sender phone number. Both should be 10 digit mobile numbers. Sender phone number should be the mobile number of whoever is responsible for handing over the package to our delivery boy, and the recipient phone number should be the mobile number of the person to whom the package should be delivered to. Package size is an integer in the range 1-9 which represents the size of the consignment.
